6395
05:02:33.925 --> 05:02:35.465
on any given day at a race,

6396
05:02:36.055 --> 05:02:39.545
dogs can suffer from broken bones, dislocations,

6397
05:02:40.005 --> 05:02:44.065
muscle tears, spinal injuries, and internal trauma.

6398
05:02:45.245 --> 05:02:46.655
Some are killed on the spot

6399
05:02:47.495 --> 05:02:49.355
and others leave the track with injuries

6400
05:02:49.355 --> 05:02:50.875
that shape the rest of their lives.

6401
05:02:52.305 --> 05:02:54.845
Our written submission focuses on this animal welfare

6402
05:02:55.165 --> 05:02:58.605
evidence, some of the data and the formal review processes.

6403
05:02:59.225 --> 05:03:02.005
But what it cannot capture is what those harms look like

6404
05:03:02.025 --> 05:03:03.205
for individual dogs.

6405
05:03:04.155 --> 05:03:07.165
Because behind every statistic is a living,

6406
05:03:07.435 --> 05:03:10.405
breathing animal whose life has been altered

6407
05:03:10.505 --> 05:03:12.365
or ended in the pursuit of profit.

6408
05:03:13.465 --> 05:03:16.045
And I'd like to briefly share a few examples

6409
05:03:16.075 --> 05:03:17.085
from the past year.

6410
05:03:18.585 --> 05:03:20.805
On March 13th, 2025,

6411
