6413
05:03:28.815 --> 05:03:31.435
Her breathing was labored, she struggled to stand.

6414
05:03:32.215 --> 05:03:34.035
We watched her fall to the ground

6415
05:03:34.655 --> 05:03:36.435
and her lifeless body carried away.

6416
05:03:37.395 --> 05:03:39.425
Veterinary assessment later determined

6417
05:03:39.425 --> 05:03:42.025
that she had suffered sudden cardiovascular collapse.

6418
05:03:42.885 --> 05:03:47.035
She was just five years old exactly three months later,

6419
05:03:47.375 --> 05:03:51.795
on the 13th of June, 2025, Homebush Fi Joa collapsed

6420
05:03:51.795 --> 05:03:52.835
and died at the law.

6421
05:03:52.835 --> 05:03:57.435
After a race, she had severe internal bleeding in her chest

6422
05:03:57.535 --> 05:04:00.915
and lungs and significant fluid buildup in her lungs.

6423
05:04:01.865 --> 05:04:04.365
Her body could no longer circulate oxygen properly,

6424
05:04:04.705 --> 05:04:06.085
and her heart and lungs failed.

6425
05:04:06.985 --> 05:04:08.605
She was just two and a half years old.

6426
05:04:09.945 --> 05:04:13.005
And then on the 28th of December, 2025,

6427
05:04:13.015 --> 05:04:15.245
while we were out enjoying the summer holidays,

6428
05:04:15.915 --> 05:04:19.085
epic pill broke both bones in her lower right four leg.

6429
05:04:19.085 --> 05:04:22.115
During a race, the fracture was open,

6430
05:04:22.385 --> 05:04:24.555
meaning the bone had pierced through the skin.

6431
05:04:25.545 --> 05:04:26.845
The injury was so severe

6432
05:04:26.845 --> 05:04:28.245
that vets concluded there was no

6433
05:04:28.245 --> 05:04:30.045
realistic prospect for recovery.

6434
05:04:31.115 --> 05:04:34.255
She was euthanized also at just two and a half years old.

6435
05:04:35.745 --> 05:04:38.775
These dogs were young, they were doing exactly

6436
05:04:38.805 --> 05:04:40.495
what they were bred and trained to do.

6437
05:04:41.515 --> 05:04:44.465
Their injuries were not freak accidents or outliers.

6438
05:04:44.815 --> 05:04:47.185
They are part of a pattern that has persisted year

6439
05:04:47.185 --> 05:04:50.745
after year, despite new rules, new audits,

6440
05:04:51.165 --> 05:04:52.425
new welfare initiatives.

6441
05:04:53.095 --> 05:04:54.665
That is the uncomfortable truth.

6442
05:04:54.845 --> 05:04:59.295
At the heart of this bill, I did want to address some

6443
05:04:59.295 --> 05:05:02.215
of the arguments the industry often raises

6444
05:05:02.215 --> 05:05:04.655
and has raised today in response to cases like these.

6445
