And this is one of the very rare animal issues

6502
05:07:55.285 --> 05:07:58.105
to attract agreement across political lines.

6503
05:07:59.285 --> 05:08:02.145
New Zealanders increasingly expect parliament

6504
05:08:02.145 --> 05:08:04.905
to act decisively when animals are being harmed

6505
05:08:04.905 --> 05:08:06.465
in predictable ways.

6506
05:08:07.605 --> 05:08:10.505
And internationally. New Zealand is not acting in isolation.

6507
05:08:11.015 --> 05:08:13.985
Greyhound racing is in sharp decline globally.

6508
05:08:14.605 --> 05:08:16.305
We are one of only five countries

6509
