7693
06:02:48.545 --> 06:02:50.085
Our dogs are loved and well cared for.

7694
06:02:50.315 --> 06:02:52.525
With our strong regulations, transparency,

7695
06:02:52.985 --> 06:02:55.765
and continued reform, their welfare can continue

7696
06:02:55.765 --> 06:02:57.645
to improve without destroying lives

7697
